{"tid":1326768,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"上訴庭重申︰不能假設警察證供特別可信","createTime":"2019-07-17T10:41:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T13:41:52.000Z","uid":271284,"like":119,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ae7db2388e4e40ea2e8df77e5c20c0382839dee2","tid":1326768,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:41:27.000Z","msg":"要破「警處襲警」指控，首先要打甩警察係誠實證人呢個前設，前年有一單案例，就係確認法庭不能前設警察口供特別可信既<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/70838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F70838&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aueF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=1d236b56\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.thenewslens.com/article/70838</a><br />\n<br />\n<em>當審訊中需要處理來自辦案警員的證供時，法官不可試圖指引陪審團，警察作為證人的供詞會比其他證人可信，或者引導陪審團以不客觀公正的方式審視警察證供，例如衡量證供價值時偏重於警察一方。此外，法官也不能在指引陪審團時斷言警察編造證供的機會較少，特別不能向陪審團提出，警察不會冒著喪失長俸與自由的危險而栽贓，或者類似效果的指引。<br />\n上訴庭指出，上述關於處理警察證供的指引，同樣適用於單一法官（或裁判官）審理案件的情況；而本案中原審法官的分析，則完全違反了終審庭與上訴庭頒佈的這些指引。鑑於控方並沒有提出其他足以定罪的理據，上訴庭就此裁定撤銷被告的全部控罪。</em><br />\n<br />\n第二，借用立場新聞既搜習既案例，證明警察比假口供已經到左泛濫既程度<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/一年-警亂作供-檢控佔領者-警員證供屢被法官指不可信-矛盾-不符影片/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%82%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B-%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E8%80%85-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B%E5%B1%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%A1-%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE-%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%2F&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aueF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=145fa3ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E8%AD%A6%E4%BA%82%E4%BD%9C%E4%BE%9B-%E6%AA%A2%E6%8E%A7%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E8%80%85-%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%89%E4%BE%9B%E5%B1%A2%E8%A2%AB%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E6%8C%87%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%AF%E4%BF%A1-%E7%9F%9B%E7%9B%BE-%E4%B8%8D%E7%AC%A6%E5%BD%B1%E7%89%87%2F&h=554274c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/一年-警亂作供-檢控佔領者-警員證供屢被法官指不可信-矛盾-不符影片/</a><br />\n<br />\n當然唔少得有曬片眾目睽睽下咁屈<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190709/59802700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190709%2F59802700&d=SosmRuku1xQpFtIKZJ5aueF5TOcUp1XGW39uuIwQJ%2Fg%3D&h=3005580c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190709%2F59802700&h=96942c7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190709/59802700</a><br />\n<br />\n加上證人同疑犯如果原先已經有過節，比既證供係更加不可信，而警察同示威者既過節真係多到數唔曬<br />\n<br />\n所以警察既舉證責任需要去到刑事案毫無合理疑點既門檻，而響警察既證供本身就係一個疑點既情況下，單憑警察既口供，根本做唔到。<br />\n<br />\n好話唔好聽，真係打左你你都告我唔入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95178eb8a0e45a50d413a5b3a3de37d56787929e","tid":1326768,"uid":264811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e81e16c7d4e78aff16c6bb360ddb1b55d8e49868","tid":1326768,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:42:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e24fc2d7dd0b992935e23b491ec20a7e24019de3","tid":1326768,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:42:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de6384bd7fe48b55e27260037bb1287de3d49da","tid":1326768,"uid":52490,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:43:51.000Z","msg":"最驚遇著彭寶琴呢類仆街"},{"pid":"fa617b1b00680f1b13b704e955ef04534ed309f2","tid":1326768,"uid":81385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:44:16.000Z","msg":"strong post lm"},{"pid":"9d30cedaa5501b26ea668225c2ed770d372d27dc","tid":1326768,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:44:17.000Z","msg":"情