Z","msg":"提返各位冇可能成為陪審員嘅毅進仔<br />\n陪審團可以唔比原因否決<br />\n<blockquote>刑事案件中的被告給賦予了陪審團審訊權是為了防止政府的壓迫&hellip;&hellip;賦予被告權力去面對由他同胞組成的陪審團來進行審訊，給了被告不可估量的防禦，來抵抗腐敗或激進的檢控官，以及抵抗喜愛附和、帶有偏見和極不尋常的法官。如果被告的首選是要面對以常識作裁決的陪審團，多於希望面對博學但缺乏同理心的一個法官，那麼被告就應該可以這樣做&hellip;&hellip;就是不要把公民的生命和自由全權委託於一個法官或一組法官身上&hellip;&hellip;</blockquote>`"},{"pid":"deddc513394dc0c23c6343e15c6835e3de52805d","tid":1326768,"uid":250951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T11:09:55.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n係時候cap底圖加字幕通街揚"},{"pid":"7828c744827c906feaaf34e06d1abcdce0d076f8","tid":1326768,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bea3c7fc8ae330512ca8be5674a55a8c7e604df","tid":1326768,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T10:51:21.000Z","msg":"想問下樓主是否有法律觀點支持<br />\n<br />\n定只係一般市民睇法？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:16:16.000Z","msg":"無法律學位但有少少法律底。打完都吿唔入完全係鳩吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"584edbef0614d77221a8b2ca887ed4e69582dd36","tid":1326768,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"以胸襲警果單點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40eac5a9af1b2032fe5d179f0939a8bea280fbb0","tid":1326768,"uid":126046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"我諗啲法官平時都見識過唔少"},{"pid":"c581214e1f7cf033ca8c795f38c3a339028f4d7a","tid":1326768,"uid":137217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584edbef0614d77221a8b2ca887ed4e69582dd36","tid":1326768,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"以胸襲警果單點計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T12:24:19.000Z","msg":"紅底法官既問題"},{"pid":"56145b2eb1ac0c537fe76111f1e2f4e0e1490582","tid":1326768,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"584edbef0614d77221a8b2ca887ed4e69582dd36","tid